==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unmask
<hw>Un*mask"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>mask</ets>.]</ety> <def>To strip of a mask or
disguise; to lay open; to expose.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unmask</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Unmask
<hw>Un*mask"</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To put off a mask.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unmasterable</ent>⟦br⟧
